column2:
"Welcome back.
You really help us a lot by completing
the work fast."

"They seem to be retreating but I'm sure
they'll be back for another round of
attack..."

"I will need your help again when the
time comes. We will keep killing them
as they appear. That will never change."

"お帰り。
迅速な仕事ぶりで助かるよ。"

"ヤツらも引き返したようだけど
またやってくるだろうね……"

"その時はまたよろしく頼むよ。
何度現れても、ヤツらを殺し続ける。
それは変わらないよ。"
